cast.overview: During an unfortunate series of events, a friend of Kung Fury is assassinated by the most dangerous kung fu master criminal of all time, Adolf Hitler, a.k.a Kung Führer.  Kung Fury decides to travel back in time to Nazi Germany in order to kill Hitler and end the Nazi empire once and for all.
cast.title: Kung Fury

details.biography: Magnus Lennarth Betnér, born August 16, 1974 in Sankt Göran's parish in Stockholm, is a Swedish comedian and actor. Since the beginning of the 2000s, Betnér has built up a national audience through participation in TV programs such as Parlamenten and Stockholm Live as well as I ditt ansikte, which he and Martin Soneby led in 2008.
details.name: Magnus Betnér
